{
  "texts": [
    "Utilizing a knowledge graph can aid in uncovering the latent semantic knowledge embedded within the content (Wang et al. 2020).",
    "The role of content in disinformation detection is undeniably significant.",
    "So, content-based features have been widely employed in the detection of disinformation.",
    "However, these features have some disadvantages.",
    "On the one hand, a limitation of content-based features is that they are often extracted from specific domains."
  ]
}